          array('lab_list_id' => '119','inventory_id' => '219','lab' => 'Agilent LC/MSD 1100','fee' => '1','guest' => '1','host' => '1','descr' => 'HPLC system equipped with vacuum degasser, binary pump, thermostatted column compartment, auto sampler and UV-Vis diode array detector (DAD). The ion trap mass spectrometer is suited for acquisition of MSn spectra and it can be acquired in full scan or single-ion monitoring modes, 50-2200 m/z range, positive and negative polarity. Available two sources: electrospray ionization (ESI) and atmospheric pressure chemical ionization (APCI). Sample introduction by LC or syringe pump.'),
