          array('lab_list_id' => '132','inventory_id' => '222','lab' => 'Single Sensillum Recording','fee' => '2','guest' => '1','host' => '1','descr' => '3 Extracellular recording systems, specifically designed for recording sensory responses from insects.  One custom system for cut-tip glass electrode recording, and 2 others using a Syntech tungsten recording system.  A Tasteprobe contact stimulus recording device is also available.  Reflected, fluorescent and stereoscopic or compound configurations are possible'),
